WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.760
Salom, Python dasturlash tili 
darslariga xush kelibsiz! 

00:00:03.760 --> 00:00:05.455
Biz bilan birga ekanligingizdan 
g‘oyat mamnunmiz.

00:00:05.455 --> 00:00:09.970
Bu kursda siz Python tilida 
dasturlashni o‘rganasiz.

00:00:09.970 --> 00:00:14.130
Bugungi kunda dunyoda juda ko‘plab 
dasturlash tillari mavjud, ammo Python 

00:00:14.130 --> 00:00:18.480
o‘rganishga oson va ishatishda qulayligi 
bilan juda mashhur bo‘lgan tildir.

00:00:18.480 --> 00:00:22.545
Python code can run on any major kind of computer today.
Python kodi bugungi kunda har qanday 
asosiy turdagi kompyuterlarda ishlashi mumkin.

00:00:22.545 --> 00:00:27.780
Windows PC va Mac dan tortib yuqori 
quvvatli Linux serveri va, hattoki, 

00:00:27.780 --> 00:00:31.110
sizning telefoningizda ham. Shuningdek, 
Python deyarli barcha sohalarda -

00:00:31.110 --> 00:00:34.850
Web development (veb islab chiqarish) va data analysis (ma’lumotlarni tahlil qilish)dan tortib to AI - sun’iy idrokgacha qo‘llaniladi.

00:00:34.850 --> 00:00:39.545
Bu yerda o‘rganadigan ko‘nikmalaringiz sizning 
dasturchi bo‘lib yetishishdagi sayohatingizda muhimdir.

00:00:39.545 --> 00:00:44.000
Ushbu darslarda o‘rganadigan ko‘plab 
tushunchalar Python bilan cheklanib qolmaydi.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:48.650
Biz dasturlashning eng fundamental 
qurilish bloklarini, 

00:00:48.650 --> 00:00:51.050
hamda dasturlashing qaysi sohasiga 
qiziqshinggizdan qat’iy nazar 

00:00:51.050 --> 00:00:54.040
barchasiga birdek foydali bo‘ladigan 
g‘oya va ko‘ikmalarni ko‘rib, o‘rganib chiqamiz.

00:00:54.040 --> 00:00:55.840
Keyingi bir necha darslarda 

00:00:55.840 --> 00:01:00.050
siz ishlatadigan dasturlar Turtle Graphics 
(Toshbaqa Grafikasi) deb nomlangan funksiyadan foydalanadi.

00:01:00.050 --> 00:01:04.490
Turtle bu ekranda rangli shakllarni chizishi 
mumkin bo‘lgan hayoliy robotdir.

00:01:04.490 --> 00:01:08.215
Bu usulda, siz, dasturingiz qanday ishni amalga 
oshirayotganini tezda aytib berishingiz mumkin.

00:01:08.215 --> 00:01:11.120
Dasturlashni o‘rganishda Python kabi 
dasturlash tilining grammatikasini o‘rganish 

00:01:11.120 --> 00:01:14.270
bir qism xolos. Dasturlash aslida, 

00:01:14.270 --> 00:01:18.145
ketma-ketliklar, takrorlanishlar, axborot va 
jarayonlar haqida fikr yuritishni o‘rganishdir. 

00:01:18.145 --> 00:01:23.280
va Turtle bizga bularni tasavvur 
qilishimizga yo‘l ochib beradi.

